Author: yknupsx
Text: I know I should, it's difficult though to find doctors where I am. but I reconnected with my nutritionist and have found a therapist for next year and my doctors thinks that because I've got them I don't need to go to her anymore, which I have absolutely no problem with so today was the last of her. it just really set me off

Author: Xgx9
Text: I'm so sorry to hear this is happening to you. It really shouldn't be. From everything you just shared, it does sound like you're ill. If I were you, I would seriously consider changing doctors (to someone who takes EDs seriously).
